About Event

​A small group of founders and marketing folks getting together over brunch to talk GTM.

​We'll dig into what's actually working, what's not, and what we're experimenting with—paid acquisition, content, product-led growth, building lean marketing teams, whatever's top of mind.

​If you're actively figuring out how to scale growth at your startup, come through.

​🍳 Brunch included
